fields.name: BlobIndexMatch
fields.description: An array of blob index tag based filters, there can be at most 10 tag filters

fields.name: BlobTypes
fields.description: An array of predefined enum values. Currently blockBlob supports all tiering and delete actions. Only delete actions are supported for appendBlob.

fields.name: PrefixMatch
fields.description: An array of strings for prefixes to be match.
